title: The Last Track Rankings
description:
Last week, we wrapped up the final track of the Red album... before we were blessed with the deluxe and vault tracks.. and by request, we rank the last tracks! Which song do we feel truly wraps up the end of an era? Join us as we rank the final tracks!
What's your track rankings? What else would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us and let us know!
